    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, always kept in the garage and pampered every single day. If you\u2019re looking for a dream ride that\u2019s basically brand new, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'd love to chat!",
