    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit maintains factory-spec compression across all cylinders and a meticulously serviced VANOS system. The chassis integrity is absolute, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and pristine bushings. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual transmission to a Variable M Differential Lock. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the telepathic turn-in these chassis are renowned for. No hydraulic leaks, zero rod bearing concerns, and a flawless undercarriage. This is an uncompromising example of naturally aspirated precision.",
      "price": 48500.0,
