      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in a flawless exterior finish with a deep, mirror-like luster and zero rock chips or blemishes. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather seats remain supple and free of any creases, while the interior still retains that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component and feature functions perfectly, and the mechanical systems have been maintained with an open-checkbook policy. We have a complete binder of service records from day one, documenting every oil change and inspection performed by certified technicians. The undercarriage is as clean as the body, showing no signs of weather exposure or wear. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle in peak condition.",
